doctype html
html(lang='en')

    head

        meta(charset='utf-8')
        meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
        meta(name='description', content='')
        meta(name='author', content='')

        title eTrove


        // Favicon
        link(rel='icon', type='image/x-icon', href='assets/favicon.ico')

        // Font Awesome icons (free version)
        script(src='https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v6.3.0/js/all.js', crossorigin='anonymous')

        // Google fonts
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat:400,700', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto+Slab:400,100,300,700', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')

        // Core theme CSS (includes Bootstrap)
        link(href='css/styles.css', rel='stylesheet')

    body#page-top

        // Navigation
        nav#mainNav.navbar.navbar-expand-lg.navbar-dark.fixed-top
            .container
                //- a.navbar-brand(href='#page-top')
                //-     img(src='assets/img/navbar-logo.svg', alt='...')
                button.navbar-toggler(type='button', data-bs-toggle='collapse', data-bs-target='#navbarResponsive', aria-controls='navbarResponsive', aria-expanded='false', aria-label='Toggle navigation')
                    | Menu
                    i.fas.fa-bars.ms-1
                #navbarResponsive.collapse.navbar-collapse
                    ul.navbar-nav.text-uppercase.ms-auto.py-4.py-lg-0
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='#services') Services
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='#about') About
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='#team') Team
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='#contact') Contact

        // Masthead
        header.masthead
            .container
                .masthead-subheading Welcome to eTrove LLC Official Website
                .masthead-heading.text-uppercase It's Nice To Meet You
                a.btn.btn-primary.btn-xl.text-uppercase(href='#services') Tell Me More

        // Services
        section#services.page-section
            .container
                .text-center
                    h2.section-heading.text-uppercase Services
                    h3.section-subheading.text-muted We built a secure and verified marketplace that enables college students to quickly buy and sell belongings with trusted users right on campus.
                .row.text-center
                    .col-md-4
                        span.fa-stack.fa-4x
                            i.fas.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x.text-primary
                            i.fas.fa-mobile-alt.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
                        h4.my-3 Appstore Application
                        p.text-muted Our secure and verified campus marketplace app is available on the App Store, enabling college students to buy and sell belongings quickly and safely with verified users.
                    .col-md-4
                        span.fa-stack.fa-4x
                            i.fas.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x.text-primary
                            i.fas.fa-globe.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
                        h4.my-3 Web Application
                        p.text-muted We’re building modern, responsive web apps with robust functionality—coming soon to elevate your business online.
                    .col-md-4
                        span.fa-stack.fa-4x
                            i.fas.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x.text-primary
                            i.fab.fa-android.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
                        h4.my-3 Android Application
                        p.text-muted We create professional, high-performance Android mobile applications optimized for usability and Google Play, coming soon.

        // About
        section#about.page-section
            .container
                .text-center
                    h2.section-heading.text-uppercase About
                ul.timeline
                    li
                        .timeline-image
                            img.rounded-circle.img-fluid(src='assets/img/about/1.jpg', alt='2021')
                        .timeline-panel
                            .timeline-heading
                                h4 2021
                            .timeline-body
                                p.text-muted
                                    | Founder Minjae Sung moved into college and saw the problem firsthand: third-party marketplaces were full of unverified profiles and scam posts. After being scammed himself, he set out to build a safer way for students to trade.
                    li.timeline-inverted
                        .timeline-image
                            img.rounded-circle.img-fluid(src='assets/img/about/2.jpg', alt='2022')
                        .timeline-panel
                            .timeline-heading
                                h4 2022
                            .timeline-body
                                p.text-muted With no budget for outside developers, Minjae taught himself to code so classmates could trade confidently with verified school emails.
                    li
                        .timeline-image
                            img.rounded-circle.img-fluid(src='assets/img/about/3.jpg', alt='2024')
                        .timeline-panel
                            .timeline-heading
                                h4 2024
                            .timeline-body
                                p.text-muted
                                    | Engineer Milan Rona joined as co-founder, rebuilding the backend for speed, security, and effortless scaling.
                    li.timeline-inverted
                        .timeline-image
                            img.rounded-circle.img-fluid(src='assets/img/about/4.jpg', alt='2025')
                        .timeline-panel
                            .timeline-heading
                                h4 2025
                            .timeline-body
                                p.text-muted Our five-person team launched Swap Door and attracted 598 students and 960 total listings in 90 days across the U.S colleges. We’re growing fast and still driven by the same mission: give every campus a trusted marketplace.

        // Team
        section#team.page-section.bg-light
            .container
                .text-center
                    h2.section-heading.text-uppercase Our Amazing Team
                    h3.section-subheading.text-muted Meet the people behind eTrove LLC.
                .row.justify-content-center
                    .col-lg-4
                        .team-member
                            img.mx-auto.rounded-circle(src='assets/img/team/1.jpg', alt='Min Jae')
                            h4 Min Jae
                            p.text-muted Founder & CEO
                            a.btn.btn-dark.btn-social.mx-2(href='#!', aria-label='Min Jae LinkedIn Profile')
                                i.fab.fa-linkedin-in
                    .col-lg-4
                        .team-member
                            img.mx-auto.rounded-circle(src='assets/img/team/2.jpg', alt='Milan Rona')
                            h4 Milan Rona
                            p.text-muted CTO
                            a.btn.btn-dark.btn-social.mx-2(href='#!', aria-label='Milan Rona LinkedIn Profile')
                                i.fab.fa-linkedin-in
                .row
                    .col-lg-8.mx-auto.text-center
                        p.large.text-muted We are passionate about building a secure and trusted marketplace for college students.

        // Clients
        div.py-5
            .container
                .row.align-items-center
                    .col-md-3.col-sm-6.my-3
                        a(href='#!')
                            img.img-fluid.img-brand.d-block.mx-auto(src='assets/img/logos/microsoft.svg', alt='...', aria-label='Microsoft Logo')
                    .col-md-3.col-sm-6.my-3
                        a(href='#!')
                            img.img-fluid.img-brand.d-block.mx-auto(src='assets/img/logos/google.svg', alt='...', aria-label='Google Logo')
                    .col-md-3.col-sm-6.my-3
                        a(href='#!')
                            img.img-fluid.img-brand.d-block.mx-auto(src='assets/img/logos/facebook.svg', alt='...', aria-label='Facebook Logo')
                    .col-md-3.col-sm-6.my-3
                        a(href='#!')
                            img.img-fluid.img-brand.d-block.mx-auto(src='assets/img/logos/ibm.svg', alt='...', aria-label='IBM Logo')

        // Contact
        section#contact.page-section
            .container
                .text-center
                    h2.section-heading.text-uppercase Contact Us
                    h3.section-subheading.text-muted We'd love to hear from you! Reach out with questions, partnership ideas, or feedback.

                // * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *
                // * * SB Forms Contact Form * *
                // * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *

                // This form is pre-integrated with SB Forms.
                // To make this form functional, sign up at
                // https://startbootstrap.com/solution/contact-forms
                // to get an API token!

                form#contactForm(data-sb-form-api-token='API_TOKEN')
                    .row.align-items-stretch.mb-5
                        .col-md-6
                            .form-group
                                input#name.form-control(type='text', placeholder='Your Name *', data-sb-validations='required')
                                .invalid-feedback(data-sb-feedback='name:required') A name is required.
                            .form-group

                                // Email address input
                                input#email.form-control(
                                    type='email',
                                    placeholder='Your Email *',
                                    data-sb-validations='required,email'
                                )
                                .invalid-feedback(data-sb-feedback='email:required')
                                    | An email is required.
                                .invalid-feedback(data-sb-feedback='email:email')
                                    | Please enter a valid email address.

                            .form-group.mb-md-0
                                input#phone.form-control(type='tel', placeholder='Your Phone *', data-sb-validations='required')
                                .invalid-feedback(data-sb-feedback='phone:required') A phone number is required.
                        .col-md-6
                            .form-group.form-group-textarea.mb-md-0
                                // Message input
                                textarea#message.form-control(
                                    placeholder='Your Message *',
                                    data-sb-validations='required'
                                )
                                .invalid-feedback(data-sb-feedback='message:required')
                                    | A message is required.

                    // Submit success message
                    #submitSuccessMessage.d-none
                        .text-center.text-white.mb-3
                            .fw-bolder Thank you for reaching out!
                            | We have received your message and will get back to you soon.
                            br
                            a(href='https://startbootstrap.com/solution/contact-forms') Learn more about our contact form integration

                    // Submit error message
                    #submitErrorMessage.d-none
                        .text-center.text-danger.mb-3 There was an error sending your message. Please try again later.

                    // Submit Button
                    .text-center
                        button#submitButton.btn.btn-primary.btn-xl.text-uppercase.disabled(type='submit') Send Message

        // Footer
        footer.footer.py-4
            .container
                .row.align-items-center
                    .col-lg-4.text-lg-start
                        | Copyright &copy; eTrove LLC 2025
                    .col-lg-4.my-3.my-lg-0
                        a.btn.btn-dark.btn-social.mx-2(href='#!', aria-label='Twitter')
                            i.fab.fa-twitter
                        a.btn.btn-dark.btn-social.mx-2(href='#!', aria-label='Facebook')
                            i.fab.fa-facebook-f
                        a.btn.btn-dark.btn-social.mx-2(href='#!', aria-label='LinkedIn')
                            i.fab.fa-linkedin-in
                    .col-lg-4.text-lg-end
                        a.link-dark.text-decoration-none.me-3(href='#!') Privacy Policy
                        a.link-dark.text-decoration-none(href='#!') Terms of Use

        // Bootstrap core JS
        script(src='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js')
        // Core theme JS
        script(src='js/scripts.js')
        // SB Forms JS
        script(src='https://cdn.startbootstrap.com/sb-forms-latest.js')
